title: British tourist screams as elephant chases Jeep | Daily Mail Online
text: show ad 'Oh God, please go!' Terrified British tourist screams as safari Jeep is chased for more than a MILE by an elephant Video filmed last month shows the elephant chasing a safari Jeep full of tourists through Kruger National Park in South Africa The woman filming the video can be heard shouting 'Oh my god' several times She later assures other passengers that their driver wouldn't put them in danger The passenger theorized that the elephant was going through musth, where male elephants experience highly aggressive behavior
